Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle of Solomon had come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Space Attack Force,\Ncommanded by Vice Admiral Dozle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...was effectively obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a defeat that the Principality of Zeon\Nhad been unable to anticipate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Degwin Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...is said to have told Gihren that\Nthis should have been expected of Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,While containing his anger\Nagainst the Sovereign...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gihren made a declaration\Nto the ranks of Zeon's high officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He would use the stronghold\Nof A Baoa Qu as the final line of defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...and defeat the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duel in Texas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to report\Nwithin the second battle line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No enemy vessels... no mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're switching in 30 minutes, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro is here now.\N- Please check his blood pressure for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar, Marker, and Amuro\Nare all holding up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard with all the things\Nthey're asking you to do, Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing compared to what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- How long has it been?\N- Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the two of us stopped talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, we've been so preoccupied.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer analysis says you're healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro... You've become so strong, it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far beyond my reach now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you being weak, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have to grow up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... Fraw Bow... I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But... did something happen at Side 6?\NIt seems you've changed, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you someday,\Nwhen I figure out what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh...\N- How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Hayato coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right on track,\Nthanks to his athletic background.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem...\NIt's the Texas shoal zone region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we wake everyone up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry to wake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Chivvay at the edge\Nof the third combat line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...there seem to be others in the Texas zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On a mopping-up operation of enemy\Nvessels that escaped from Solomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base enters the Texas zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a shoal zone filled with debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This colony was originally built\Nfor leisure and raising livestock...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was named Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was abandoned due to\Nits lack of military significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now surrounded by drifting rocks\Nand colony debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't the Elmeth and bits\Nbeen delivered to Texas yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The fine-tuning is taking some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.\NAt least my own Gelgoog has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone here at Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there are some former workers\Nand staff at the colony's management office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So the colony is practically uninhabited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Trojan Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- M'Quve is nearby?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no weapons on hand,\Nso let him deal with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be docking the Zanzibar at Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chivvay is moving.\NThey've noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Wake up the whole crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy approaching!\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All hands to level 3 battle stations!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such a nice bath, especially\Nafter barely escaping with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy probably escaped from Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll launch the Guncannon\Nas soon as we reach the second battle area!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, we may have survived\NSolomon, but stay on guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to work and get tired a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for you, if you ever want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...\NIt's good to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I'd planned.\NWe've found the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uragang! What's the status of my Gyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... Proceed now to Area Two,\Nthen launch the Rick Doms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sortie with my Gyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no reason you should\Ngo out in person, Captain M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, yes there is.\N- Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit Gyan was developed\Nespecially for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I must maintain my standing as a man\Nto Rear Admiral Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I hear that Char still\Nhasn't received the mobile suit he requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll demolish the Trojan Horse\Nand the Gundam while he watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to locate the Chivvay\Nin the second battle area. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trojan Horse detected In Point 3-AA!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All hands to battle stations!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rick Doms, make a preemptive strike{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the Gundam,\Nlure it into Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll make it easier for the Gyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir! We understand.\N- Good! Then move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come... Ms. Sayla, the Chivvay!\NIt'll come into view soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker, what are the enemy's movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to see through the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum magnification ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the enemy after the G-Armor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uragang! I'm counting on you\Nto stall the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one ship,\Nbut don't relax your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Captain. All clear for takeoff, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do everything as per the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set a trap near Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, it's a two-rank promotion\Nif we defeat the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See that, Amuro?\NAre there 4 or 5 mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Minovsky particles\Nand all the rocks, it's hard to tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, can you shoot them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry and bolt out!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam and G-Fighter\Nare drifting toward Texas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Standby to take off!\NAll hands to level 1 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Petty Officer Sunmalo.\NHas another battle begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just concentrate on getting better, Hayato.\NThat's part of your duty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that, but my injuries\Naren't as bad as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be up and about in a couple of days,\Nso just rest up until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to be a dashing hero, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look dashing as a healthy patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make things difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This colony's a sad sight\Nwith its mirror adjustment problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, Flanagan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing well. Lalah hit the test targets\Nwith 70 percent accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we should return to the Zanzibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at the Texas colony,\Nbuilt for cattle raising and leisure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...the mirrors were damaged in the war,\Nand stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The colony has remained in twilight\Nfor over 8 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The land has thus turned to desert,\Nand the people have moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's coming.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming here? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I sensing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Flanagan! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not one of the test targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her brain waves resonate\Nlike this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there somebody like me around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like you touched my heart, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That tingling sensation just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pilots are experienced!\NBut I can read their pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam and G-Fighter\Nhave entered the Texas area!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the starboard fleet doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No changes. They're progressing slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing was a scheme\Nto lure me toward this mobile suit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me... Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about devious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for expecting everyone\Nto fight fair and square, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's escaping into Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At you, Captain. Does that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I can pilot the Elmeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just have to get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll be a better pilot than me\Nin no time, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than the Red Comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I wouldn't have sent\Nan orphan like you to the Flanagan Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I left you feeling lonely at Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Captain M'Quve has entered Texas\Nin his mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve? How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew he had this side to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's had a mobile suit developed\Nfor his own personal use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he's sworn to bring down\Nthe Trojan Horse. He must feel confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's simply trying to spite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of any other reason\Nfor him to do something so foolhardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless...\Nwe can't sit still and watch, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gelgoog's maintenance is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a prototype, so it's hardly perfect, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this will double as a field test\Nwhile I keep an eye on M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy vessels!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! Send out the Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- How many vessels, Marker?\N- One Chivvay, two Musais!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I've memorized the data\Non the Gelgoog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you at least wear a normal suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my policy to come back\Nwith my mobile suit in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I rely on my survival instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I never wear combat suits\Nor normal suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take me up!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These small-scale bombs won't hurt me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Observe from a safe distance, Lalah..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then. Show me what you've got, M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1... Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baromel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Use those rocks to shield the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have good instincts,\Nor is he one of those new types of human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A friendly mobile suit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A red mobile suit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your mission\Nto defeat the Gundam right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand idly by\Nand ignore an ally in obvious trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own way of fighting!\NThat's why I lured the Gundam here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you, Captain M'Quve.\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed it with the data I've collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've used up too much beam energy\Nin your skirmish with Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that the Gundam\Nwould get rid of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But M'Quve's putting up a good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah, you're watching this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't the Captain go and help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same thing I felt earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your sword away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dirty tricks are no match\Nagainst Gundam's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to put Char in his place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have to defeat the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop already. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uragang! Deliver that antique vase\Nto Lady Kycilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So hastily prepared, you can't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A... mu... ro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,La... lah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For Amuro, who is on the verge\Nof acquiring a new strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...Char poses virtually no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As the fierce battle continues,\NSayla asks Char in earnest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he leave Zeon behind\Nand finally return to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NChar and Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Char and Sayla
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:54.07,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:59.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:09.29,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:14.22,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.85,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.23,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:28.82,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:39.12,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.23,0:23:54.07,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:59.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:09.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:14.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:18.85,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:28.82,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:39.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
